            "description": "<div id=\"newsBody\">\n<span class=\"newsDetail\" style=\"font-size: 13px; font-family:MingLiu;Arial;\">  部份电动车股受压，小鹏汽车(09868)现造78.1元，回吐3.7%。理想汽车(02015)报89.95元，跌3.07%。比亚迪股份(01211)报371.2元，跌1.28%。<br/><br/>吉利汽车(00175)暂跌0.48%。 (SY)</span>\n</div>",
